Per [http://download.level1.com/level1/member/marketingdocument/Broadband_and_ADSL_Router_Comparison_Table.xls LevelOne's comparison table], this is Marvell based.
OEM SerComm, looks to be identical to the [[Belkin F5D7230-4 v6]]
Per [http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?p=407119 this DD-WRT forums thread], the FCC ID is ULT540558060901.
The default SSID is '''default'''.
